/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f7a3f667e1e38b6caf96b955274d35209149972","tid":1999241,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T07:30:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f349c943a44ab412edd298b4a716d6b49e48b4","tid":1999241,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T08:49:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"630dc8bf55ab01563114bdaafd4f4416682f8559","tid":1999241,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T00:37:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />早"},{"pid":"1bb18d36f2bfc7d045c9bd2c465e244ca93d4979","tid":1999241,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T00:39:25.000Z","msg":"一黨專政<br />\n一台獨大"},{"pid":"70292be5bce41172885000517a0688d7f65f5b36","tid":1999241,"uid":155137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd295af044356a1b857584a3f25dba01b2b5a47a","tid":1999241,"uid":188,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T04:52:36.000Z","msg":"要百姓用國貨自己拿哎鳳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T00:44:27.000Z","msg":"國產貨咁優秀 都優先讓給民眾了<br />\n領導只能被逼用次等外國貨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb2817a2555b67bf7e8418ce3f80ff6c7dab525","tid":1999241,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T00:55:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fac